{"tid":2036204,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天寄語抗爭者 : 只有眼前路，沒有何鴻燊","createTime":"2020-05-26T10:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T01:03:51.000Z","uid":202348,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57bf8432c84a65134c1ff4e97c0e891218fb3c55","tid":2036204,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"警方昨晚突擊搜查火炭坳背灣街喜利佳工業大廈一個單位，檢獲一批攻擊性武器及懷疑汽油彈等，拘捕7男1女，當中包括已被取締的民族黨召集人陳浩天。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">陳浩天透過律師表示：「無懼白色恐怖，唔好怕俾人拉，只有眼前路，沒有何鴻燊。」</span><br />\n<br />\n有示威者先後包圍沙田警署及馬鞍山警署，要求釋放被捕人士，防暴警察在馬鞍山驅散示威者，凌晨3時後事件平息。"},{"pid":"cb326c34a5f7279deb937ea1c9d92885cddd50dd","tid":2036204,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2208512/陳浩天被捕%3A只有眼前路+沒有身後身\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2208512%2F%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%253A%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%9C%BC%E5%89%8D%E8%B7%AF%2B%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%BA%AB%E5%BE%8C%E8%BA%AB&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=30b352ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2208512/陳浩天被捕%3A只有眼前路+沒有身後身</a>"},{"pid":"a2690188c61dc98127e61373ff3433be621a40c4","tid":2036204,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"牙天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ba72cfc7599c8fb887869bcc61fb3810358627","tid":2036204,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm